><br />综上，没有一款完美的满足要求，求大神们推荐。", "last_modified": 1612366722, "replies": 126, "id": 751085}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_large.png?m=1598508742", "name": "shenzhen", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_normal.png?m=1598508742", "title": "深圳", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen", "topics": 2027, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shenzhen", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1598508742", "stars": 1457, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 21, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"username": "jatsz2020", "website": null, "github": null, "psn": null, "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bfa7/4dbe/523622_mini.png?m=1607863225", "bio": null, "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jatsz2020", "tagline": null, "twitter": null, "created": 1607863124, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bfa7/4dbe/523622_mini.png?m=1607863225", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/bfa7/4dbe/523622_mini.png?m=1607863225", "location": null, "btc": null, "id": 523622}, "last_reply_by": "meteor957", "last_touched": 1612442465, "title": "菜市场居然比超市更贵？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/751074", "created": 1612362099, "content": "住的地方有菜市场，还有很多生鲜超市，一直以为菜市场便宜，所以都是在菜市场买菜，也从来没问价格。\r\n后来某天去超市偶尔听到有人说，这里的菜便宜。所以我就去调研了一下，发现菜市场确实贵。\r\n\r\n比如西红柿，菜市场的摊位我挨个问了，都是 5 元一斤，而超市是 1.9 ～ 3.9 。\r\n\r\n这是为啥？菜市场的菜更新鲜？", "content_rendered": "住的地方有菜市场，还有很多生鲜超市，一直以为菜市场便宜，所以都是在菜市场买菜，也从来没问价格。<br />后来某天去超市偶尔听到有人说，这里的菜便宜。所以我就去调研了一下，发现菜市场确实贵。<br /><br />比如西红柿，菜市场的摊位我挨个问了，都是 5 元一斤，而超市是 1.9 ～ 3.9 。<br /><br />这是为啥？菜市场的菜更新鲜？", "last_modified": 1612362099, "replies": 112, "id": 751074}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1594743680", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1594743680", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 168255, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alt